{"kanda":6,"sarga":109,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"ततःप्रवृत्तंसुक्रूरंरामरावणयोस्तदा ।सुमहदद्वैरथंयुद्धंसर्वलोकभयावहम्","trans":"Then there ensued a fierce duel between Rama and Ravana that was fearsome to the whole world.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereupon"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"रामरावणयोः","m":"for Rama and Ravana"},{"d":"सुक्रूरम्","m":"fierce"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"great"},{"d":"सर्वलोकभयावहम्","m":"fearsome to the whole world"},{"d":"धैरथम्","m":"duel"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"प्रवृत्तम्","m":"ensued"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ततोराक्षससैन्यं च हरीणां च महद्बलम् ।प्रगृहीतप्रहरणंनिश्चेष्टंसमवर्तत","trans":"Then, both Rakshasa army and huge Vanara army, stood motionless holding their weapons ready.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"राक्षससैन्यं च","m":"Rakshasa army"},{"d":"हरीणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"महत्","m":"huge"},{"d":"बलं च","m":"army"},{"d":"प्रगृहीतप्रहरणम्","m":"holding their weapons readily"},{"d":"निश्चेचष्टम्","m":"motionless"},{"d":"समवर्तत","m":"stood"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सम्प्रयुद्धेतुतौदृष्टवाबलवन्नरराक्षसौ ।व्याक्षिप्तहदृयास्सर्वेपरंविस्मयमागताः","trans":"Then, when the mighty human and the Rakshasa were both engaged in the battle, distracted at heart, all experienced supreme wonderment.","words":[{"d":"सम्प्रयुद्धौ","m":"engaged in battle"},{"d":"तौ","m":"both"},{"d":"बलवन्नरराक्षसौ","m":"mighty human and Rakshasa"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"to see"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"व्याक्षिप्तहृदयैः","m":"distracted in heart"},{"d":"परम्","m":"supreme"},{"d":"विस्मयम्","m":"wonderment"},{"d":"आगताः","m":"experienced"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"नाप्रहरणैर्व्यग्रैर्भुजैर्विस्मितबुद्धयः ।तस्थुःप्रेक्षय च सर्वेतेनाभिजग्मुःपरस्परम्","trans":"All the army on both sides lifted their hands up, holding different kinds of implements, and were amazed looking at them and did not attack one another.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"नानाप्रहरणैः","m":"different kinds of implements"},{"d":"व्यग्रैः","m":"lifted up"},{"d":"भु