d by Rama, even Ravana released arrows up to the sky. With the arrows released by both of them, the space became resplendent and by the network of arrows covering it seemed like another sky.","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"स्वशरैः","m":"those arrows"},{"d":"खम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"निरन्तरम्","m":"upto"},{"d":"चक्रे","m":"released"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"ताभ्याम्","m":"both of them"},{"d":"प्रमुक्तेन","m":"released by"},{"d":"भास्वता","m":"resplendent"},{"d":"शरवर्षेण","m":"by the rain of arrows"},{"d":"भास्वत्","m":"resplendent"},{"d":"अम्भरम्","m":"space"},{"d":"शरबद्धम्","m":"enveloped network of arrows"},{"d":"द्वितीयम् इव","m":"like"},{"d":"अभाति","m":"seemed"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"तान् दृष्टवारावणश्चक्रेस्वशरैःखंनिरन्तरम् ततस्थाभ्यांप्रमुक्तेनशरवर्षेणभास्वता ।शरबद्धमिवाभातिद्वितीयंभास्वदम्भरम्","trans":"Seeing the arrows in the sky released by Rama, even Ravana released arrows up to the sky. With the arrows released by both of them, the space became resplendent and by the network of arrows covering it seemed like another sky.","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"तान्","m":"them"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"स्वशरैः","m":"those arrows"},{"d":"खम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"निरन्तरम्","m":"upto"},{"d":"चक्रे","m":"released"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"ताभ्याम्","m":"both of them"},{"d":"प्रमुक्तेन","m":"released by"},{"d":"भास्वता","m":"resplendent"},{"d":"शरवर्षेण","m":"by the rain of arrows"},{"d":"भास्वत्","m":"resplendent"},{"d":"अम्भरम्","m":"space"},{"d":"शरबद्धम्","m":"enveloped network of arrows"},{"d":"द्वितीयम् इव","m":"like"},{"d":"अभाति","m":"seemed"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"नानिमित्तोऽभवद्भाणोनानिर्भेत्ता न निष्फलः ।अन्योन्यमभिसम्हत्यनिपेतुर्धरणीतले तथाविसृजतोर्भाणान् रामरावणयोर्मृथे ।","trans":"The arrows released by both Rama and Ravana were without result. None failed to reach the target. None failed to complete the target. The arrows were colliding with one another and fell on the ground.","words":[{"d":"मृथे","m":"in vain"},{"d":"रामरावणयोः","m":"both Rama's and Ravana's"},{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"बाणान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विसृजतोः","m":"let go"},{"d":"अनिमित्तः","m":"failed to reach the target"},{"d":"बाणः","m":"arrow"},{"d":"न अभवत्","m":"not become"},{"d":"अनिर्भेत्ता","m":"no arrow failed to complete the target"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"निष्फलः","m":"without result"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"अभिसम्हत्य","m":"colliding with each other"},{"d":"धरणीतले","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"निपेतुः","m":"fell"}]},{"v":26,"dev":"प्रायुध्येतामविच्छिन्नमस्यन्तौसव्यदक्षिणम् चक्रतुश्चशरैर्घोरैर्निरुच्छवासमिवाम्बरम् ।","trans":"Discharging from right and left, the two heroes without break vehemently released dreadful arrows that covered the sky and left no breathing space between them.","words":[{"d":"सव्यदक्षिणम्","m":"right and left direction"},{"d":"अविच्छिन्नम्","m":"without break"},{"d":"अस्यन्तौ","m":"vehemently"},{"d":"प्रायुध्येताम्","m":"discharging"},{"d":"घोरैः","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"अम्बरम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"निरुच्छवासमिव","m":"without space for breathing"},{"d":"चक्रतुः च","m":"released"}]},{"v":27,"dev":"रावणस्यहयान्रामोहयान्रामस्यरावणः जघ्नतुस्तौतदान्योन्यंकृतानुकृतकारिणौ ।","trans":"Ravana struck Rama's horses and Rama struck Ravana's horses blow to blow at that time.","words":[{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"हयान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"हयान्","m":"horses"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"तौ","m":"both"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"अन्योन्यम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"कृतानुकृतकारिणौ","m":"each other blow to blow"},{"d":"जघ्नतुः","m":"struck"}]},{"v":28,"dev":"एवंतुतौसुसङ्क्रुद्धौचक्रतुर्युद्धमुत्तमम् मुहूर्तमभवद्युद्धंतुमुलंरोमहर्षणम् ।","trans":"Both became furious in that way and the best duel took place for a moment that was fierce and horipulating.","words":[{"d":"सुसङ्क्रुद्धौ","m":"very furious"},{"d":"त